item.title: CVE-2017-3746|2024-09-17T00:11:51.684Z -- lenovo%20group%20ltd. -- thinkpad%20usb%203.0%20ethernet%20adapter%20driver
item.description: ThinkPad USB 3.0 Ethernet Adapter (part number 4X90E51405) driver, various versions, was found to contain a privilege escalation vulnerability that could allow a local user to execute arbitrary code with administrative or system level privileges.
